data.description: Welcome to 2839 Redland Trail, a stunning property located in the heart of San Antonio, TX. This luxurious home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and an abundance of modern amenities that make it the perfect place to call home. As you enter the property, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer that leads into a spacious living area with high ceilings and plenty of natural light. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of storage.
